-- RCS Capital to buy broker-dealer Cetera for $1.15 bln in cash
-- By Avik Das in Bangalore
-- Thu Jan 16, 2014 11:37AM EST
-- None



Jan 16 (Reuters) - RCS Capital Corp <RCAP.N> said it would buy independent broker-dealer Cetera Financial Group for about $1.15 billion in cash to grow its retail distribution business.

RCS Capital is buying Cetera from private equity firm Lightyear Capital LLC.